data.description: Welcome Home! You do not want to miss an opportunity to own this charming home in a quiet neighborhood. As you pull in you will notice the oversized driveway that pulls into the back. There have been many outdoor game nights in the backyard. When you enter the front door you will notice the tall ceilings and 2 skylights in the living room. The kitchen gives off a homey feel with the space to make many memories with your friends and family. The large master bedroom is downstairs and holds dual closets. There is one more oversized bedroom downstairs and a bathroom. Upstairs you will have a decent sized sitting area, bathroom, and another secondary bedroom! I could go on and on about the many things to love about this home in the heart of Hilltop but nothing I say would do justice to the warmth feeling of peace and homeyness you get when entering through the doors of 4508 Jamaica Place.
